name: Trump's Golden Bull
description: Trump's Golden Bull is not just a statue; it's a symbol of prosperity, optimism, and a nod to Trump's influence in the financial world. Crafted from gold, this larger-than-life figure aims to become the iconic mascot for the upcoming crypto bull run. It embodies the hope for growth, rallying crypto enthusiasts. Join the movement! We are forming the most Bullish community this space has ever seen! Join The bulls Join the cult.
